### POC Layout Dinamico - catalogo de requests (REST Client / VS Code)
### Todas as rotas (exceto /health e /auth/login) exigem Authorization: Bearer <token>.
### Faca o login abaixo primeiro; o token e reaproveitado via {{login.response.body.token}}.
### Usuarios demo: admin/admin123 (tudo+PII) · editor/editor123 · viewer/viewer123

@base = http://localhost:3000

### ============================ AUTENTICACAO ================================

# @name login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenant": "default", "username": "admin", "password": "admin123" }

###
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

# @name loginViewer
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenant": "default", "username": "viewer", "password": "viewer123" }

###
@viewerToken = {{loginViewer.response.body.token}}

### Login de outro tenant (isolamento VPD)
# @name loginAcme
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tenant": "acme", "username": "admin", "password": "admin123" }

###
@acmeToken = {{loginAcme.response.body.token}}

### Sem token -> 401
GET {{base}}/registros

### ============================ REGISTROS ===================================

### Cria (obrigatorios + opcionais + campos EXTRAS + lista + condicional)
POST {{base}}/registros
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "nome": "Maria Silva",
  "email": "maria.silva@example.com",
  "rendaMensal": 7500,
  "estadoCivil": "CASADO",
  "nomeConjuge": "Joao",
  "telefones": ["11999998888", "1133334444"],
  "corPreferida": "azul"
}

### Invalido (sem cpf, enum invalido, item de lista invalido) -> 422
POST {{base}}/registros
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nome": "Jo", "estadoCivil": "NAMORANDO", "telefones": ["abc"] }

### Lista paginada
GET {{base}}/registros?limit=10&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View MASCARADA (viewer: sem papel pii -> cpf/email/renda mascarados)
GET {{base}}/registros/1/view
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}

### View REVELADA (admin: papel pii) + rotulos em ingles + gera READ_SENSITIVE
GET {{base}}/registros/1/view?lang=en
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Registro cru (core + attrs; sensiveis mascarados p/ quem nao tem pii)
GET {{base}}/registros/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update com concorrencia otimista (If-Match = rowVersion atual)
PUT {{base}}/registros/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
If-Match: 1

{ "cpf": "12345678901", "nome": "Maria Silva Souza", "rendaMensal": 8200 }

### Historico de alteracoes
GET {{base}}/registros/1/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Soft-delete
DELETE {{base}}/registros/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====================== RBAC (papeis) =====================================

### viewer tenta criar -> 403
POST {{base}}/registros
Authorization: Bearer {{viewerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "cpf": "55566677700", "nome": "Nao pode" }

### ====================== ISOLAMENTO MULTI-TENANT (VPD) =====================

### default lista (nao ve registros de acme)
GET {{base}}/registros?limit=200
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### acme lista (nao ve registros de default)
GET {{base}}/registros?limit=200
Authorization: Bearer {{acmeToken}}

### ====================== FORM / GOVERNANCA =================================

### Schema do formulario (i18n, visibleWhen, itemType)
GET {{base}}/form-definition?lang=en
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Campos pendentes de aprovacao (do ATTRS, sem metadado)
GET {{base}}/pending-fields
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Aprovar um campo pendente (editor/admin)
POST {{base}}/metadata
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "logicalName": "corPreferida", "label": "Cor preferida", "dataType": "STRING", "displayOrder": 200 }

### Ignorar um campo pendente
POST {{base}}/ignored-fields
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "logicalName": "instagram" }

### ====================== VERSIONAMENTO (admin) ============================

### Lista versoes (do tenant)
GET {{base}}/layout-versions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cria DRAFT clonando a v1
POST {{base}}/layout-versions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "label": "Draft v2", "cloneFrom": 1 }

### Campos de uma versao (editor)
GET {{base}}/layout-versions/2/fields
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Edita um campo da DRAFT (admin) - troque o fieldId
PUT {{base}}/metadata/99
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "required": true, "sensitive": true, "maskStyle": "partial" }

### Diff entre versoes
GET {{base}}/layout-versions/diff?from=1&to=2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Exporta um layout (bundle portavel)
GET {{base}}/layout-versions/1/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Preview de import (diff + conflitos)
POST {{base}}/layout-versions/import/preview
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "bundle": { "formatVersion": 1, "sourceLabel": "staging", "fields": [
  { "logicalName": "rendaMensal", "jsonPath": "$.rendaMensal", "storage": "DYNAMIC", "dataType": "STRING",
    "required": 0, "visible": 1, "editable": 1, "displayOrder": 40, "label": "Renda", "active": 1 } ] } }

### Import com conflito -> 409 (sem allowConflicts)
POST {{base}}/layout-versions/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "bundle": { "formatVersion": 1, "sourceLabel": "staging", "fields": [
  { "logicalName": "rendaMensal", "jsonPath": "$.rendaMensal", "storage": "DYNAMIC", "dataType": "STRING",
    "required": 0, "visible": 1, "editable": 1, "displayOrder": 40, "label": "Renda", "active": 1 } ] } }

### Ativa uma versao
POST {{base}}/layout-versions/2/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====================== AUDITORIA / DASHBOARD / HEALTH ====================

### Trilha (filtros combinaveis)
GET {{base}}/audit?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Acessos a dado sensivel (LGPD)
GET {{base}}/audit?action=READ_SENSITIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard consolidado
GET {{base}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Healthcheck profundo (publico; checa o Oracle)
GET {{base}}/health
